comment: Vincom Hung Vuong - Can Tho - The supermarket is quite big during holidays and is decorated beautifully so people can take pictures, but the number of customers coming here is not large. - The supermarket is located on Hung Vuong street, opposite Hung Vuong park. Supermarkets are easy to find because there are many signs and advertisements along the streets. - The supermarket inside is very large and has many floors. It's very cool inside. Before, I exercised at the park or came here to go to the toilet. The toilet was very clean, always fragrant and shiny. - Most visitors to the supermarket do not go shopping but mainly come here to use services such as eating, watching movies, having fun... BECAUSE here, in my opinion, they sell high quality goods. So the price is very high so there are not many customers. - The quality of service here is excellent from the security guards, cleaning staff to service staff, all do their jobs very well, are happy and enthusiastic, I am very satisfied with their service. supermarket employee.
